urally Fair brand; cold cream under the Emami Malai Kesar Cold Cream brand; and deep moisturizing cream under the Emami Pure Glow brand. Emami Limited was founded in 1974 and is headquartered in Kolkata, India.", "fullTimeEmployees": 3217, "companyOfficers": [{"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Radhe Shyam Goenka B.Com., L.L.B., M.Com. LLB", "age": 78, "title": "Founder & Non-Executive Chairman", "yearBorn": 1947, "fiscalYear": 2025, "totalPay": 1100000, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Harsha Vardhan Agarwal B.Com.", "age": 49, "title": "MD & Vice Chairman", "yearBorn": 1976, "fiscalYear": 2025, "totalPay": 85572000, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Mohan  Goenka B.Com., M.B.A.", "age": 52, "title": "Vice Chairman & Whole Time Director", "yearBorn": 1973, "fiscalYear": 2025, "totalPay": 85572000, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Radhe Shyam Agarwal F.C.A., FCS, L.L.B., M.Com", "age": 79, "title": "Founder & Chairman Emeritus", "yearBorn": 1946, "fiscalYear": 2025, "totalPay": 200000, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Sushil Kumar Goenka B.Com.", "age": 69, "title": "Whole-Time Director", "yearBorn": 1956, "fiscalYear": 2025, "totalPay": 50616000, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Prashant  Goenka B.Com., M.B.A.", "age": 52, "title": "Whole-Time Director", "yearBorn": 1973, "fiscalYear": 2025, "totalPay": 48400000, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Ms. Priti A. Sureka B.A.", "age": 53, "title": "Whole Time Director", "yearBorn": 1972, "fiscalYear": 2025, "totalPay": 48400000, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValue": 0}, {"maxAge": 1, "name": "Mr. Naresh Hiralal Bhansali F.C.A.", "age": 59, "title": "CEO of Finance, Strategy & Business Development and CFO", "yearBorn": 1966, "fiscalYear": 2025, "totalPay": 29718000, "exercisedValue": 0, "unexercisedValu